---
const cafeteriaSlides = [
  "/assets/2016_09_cafeteria_fondo.jpg",
  "/assets/2017_07_slide_cafeteria_7.jpg",
  "/assets/2017_07_slide_cafeteria_12.jpg",
  "/assets/2017_08_slide_cafeteria_13.jpg",
  "/assets/2017_07_slide_cafeteria_10.jpg",
  "/assets/2017_07_slide_cafeteria_8.jpg",
];

const cafeteriaLogo = "/assets/2017_06_cafeteria_logo@2x-253x300.png";
---

<section class="cafe-feature">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">
    <div
      class="relative min-h-80 overflow-hidden md:min-h-128"
      aria-label="Galería de Flor de Café"
    >
      {
        cafeteriaSlides.map((src, index) => (
          <img
            src={src}
            alt={`Flor de Café, cafetería en Xico, Veracruz - ${index + 1}`}
            class="cafe-feature__slide absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
            style={`animation-delay: ${index * 5}s;`}
            loading="lazy"
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <div class="flex min-h-80 items-center bg-[#eee4d8] px-6 py-14 md:min-h-128 md:px-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center">
        <img
          src={cafeteriaLogo}
          alt="Flor de Café - Cafetería & Pastelería"
          class="mx-auto mb-8 h-auto w-28 md:w-44"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <p class="mb-6 font-display text-xl italic text-ink md:text-2xl">
          Un café es siempre una buena idea.
        </p>
        <p class="m-0 font-light text-ink">
          Su ambiente acogedor y la belleza del lugar hacen de Flor de Café, un espacio ideal para
          disfrutar un buen café en compañía de tu pareja, amigos o familiares. Comparte tu momento
          con un delicioso postre o pastel elaborados en casa.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cafe-feature__slide {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: cafe-fade 30s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes cafe-fade {
    0%,
    13% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    17%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .cafe-feature__slide {
      animation: none;
    }

    .cafe-feature__slide:not(:first-child) {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
